videos.description: Florida QB Austin Appleby's pass to C'yontai Lewis is incomplete as Florida State stops the Gators on fourth-and-goal in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Seminoles stop Gators on fourth-and-goal

videos.description: Austin Appleby sacked by Josh Sweat, fumbles the ball and recovered by DeMarcus Walker
videos.headline: Seminoles force fumble to set up prime field position

videos.description: Florida State RB Dalvin Cook finds a hole and attacks the end zone for a 17-yard rushing touchdown in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Dalvin Cook takes the rock for a 17-yard TD
Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher hints at possible placekicker change in 2nd half

videos.description: Florida manages to block Florida State's 44-yard field goal attempt prior to halftime and avoid the Seminoles taking a bigger lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida's special teams come up big with FG block) 2016/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Florida's special teams come up big with FG block
Florida head coach Jim McElwain looking for some explosive plays from his team

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass intercepted by Chauncey Gardner and returned 15 yds to the FSU 27
videos.headline: Florida interception sets up Gators in FSU territory

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Travis Rudolph for 46 yd TD and 17-6 lead
videos.headline: Travis Rudolph 46 yd TD reception expands FSU lead

videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois lasers a 46-yard pass to WR Travis Rudolph and finishes the play with a touchdown, giving the Seminoles a 17-6 lead over the Gators in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Seminoles stroll into the end zone

videos.description: Florida State's Freddie Stevenson receives the snap and hits a wall but stays on his feet to finish a 27-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter against Florida.
videos.headline: Seminoles turn on cruise control with 27-yard TD

videos.description: Florida State WR Nyqwan Murray drops a punt return and Florida DB Marcell Harris recovers the loose ball, taking it to the house for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida's special teams score off of loose ball

videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois takes the snap and runs into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown to give the Seminoles a 31-13 lead over Florida.
videos.headline: Francois' 8-yard TD run seals the deal for Florida State

videos.description: Florida State coach Jimbo Fisher explains how proud he is of his team while RB Dalvin Cook gives credit to his offensive line and receivers for big blocks to open up rushing lanes.
videos.headline: Fisher and Cook both proud with team
Breakdown of Florida State's 31-13 win over Florida
